# Input

```md
a*b*c

a_b_c

*foo*

_foo_

(*foo*)

![foo *bar*]

[foo *bar*]: train.jpg "train & tracks"

![*foo* bar][]

[*foo* bar]: /url "title"

![foo *bar*][foobar]

[FOOBAR]: train.jpg "train & tracks"

_*foo bar baz bim bam*_

*(*foo*)*

_foo _bar_ baz_

__foo_ bar_

*foo *bar**

*foo [*bar*](/url)*

*foo _bar* baz_

*foo __bar *baz bim__ bam*

```


